{
  "id": "adv_event_2309_01_04_02",
  "title": "優し過ぎます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "司会者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「REI♡HARU」またしても快勝～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "REI♡HARU wins again~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.7999829214,
      "endTime": 4.2755029265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "司会者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "破竹の勢いで準決勝に駒を進めました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re advancing to the semifinals with unstoppable momentum!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2755029265,
      "endTime": 7.868100826099999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1166495881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか怜ちゃん、いつもより息が上がっている気が\nするけど、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ I feel like you’re more out of breath than usual.\nAre you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1666495881,
      "endTime": 15.3792499473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.7621368648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。遙子さんこそ途中でバテないで下さいね\nそれより……次はあの二人が相手ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine. You should be more worried about yourself‚ Haruko-san.\nMore importantly… Our next opponents are those two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7621368648,
      "endTime": 26.3055612803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5159464757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. We have to give it our all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5159464757,
      "endTime": 29.270844356300003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5145799715
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 30.5878941457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "司会者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、やってきました準決勝！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ it’s time for the semifinals!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3478677352,
      "endTime": 34.9069439337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob3",
      "speakerName": "司会者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「REI♡HARU」、よろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "REI♡HARU‚ please give it your best~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9069439337,
      "endTime": 38.6278677543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8145344019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "（私達は十分努力してきた。あれだけ頑張ってきて）\n（負ける訳……あれ……立ち眩み……?）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We’ve put in enough effort. We’ve worked so hard‚）\n（there’s no way we’ll lose… Huh… I’m feeling dizzy…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8145344019,
      "endTime": 51.2033779383,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14291.522488200002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1060568901
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7471493641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん大丈夫！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ are you okay!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7471493641,
      "endTime": 57.747149411799995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9575346072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫です……続けましょう……！\n遙子さんは自分の立ち位置に……戻って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m okay… Let’s continue… !\nHaruko-san‚ get back to your… position!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9575346072,
      "endTime": 67.5851085742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "（くっ……ステージ上でいつまでも倒れている訳には）\n（いかないのに……体が重くて……動かせない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh… I can’t just… collapse on stage…）\n（But my body’s so heavy… I can’t move…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0954937696,
      "endTime": 79.62649180870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8368770041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "……怜ちゃん、ダメよ\nすみません！　私達……棄権します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rei‚ stop.\nI’m sorry! We… give up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8368770041,
      "endTime": 89.3151759542,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4849.53033139999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.5255611497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……ど、どうしてですか！？　私はまだやれます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what…? W-why!? I can still dance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5255611497,
      "endTime": 94.7255612451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9359464405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "いいから。まずは救護室に行きましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. Let’s head to the infirmary‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9359464405,
      "endTime": 98.5076470612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7680322565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "良かったわね、軽く足をくじいただけで済んだみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad it looks like you just sprained your ankle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8180322565,
      "endTime": 105.5144269861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.7248121815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで……なんで止めたんですか！？\nこれくらいの怪我なら、私はまだ踊れたのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why… Why did you stop me!?\nI could’ve kept dancing with an injury like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7248121815,
      "endTime": 113.49794145390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.7083266494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの。一度きりの勝負より\n怜ちゃんの体の方が大事に決まってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? Your health is more important\nthan a one-time match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7083266494,
      "endTime": 120.4004808662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.6108660615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "一度きりの勝負だって分かってるんじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know this was a one-time match!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6108660615,
      "endTime": 124.15086607100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.3612512664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは優し過ぎます！　そんなんじゃ……\n一生、トップアイドルになんてなれないのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too kind‚ Haruko-san! At this rate…\nwe’ll never become top idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3612512664,
      "endTime": 132.1612512663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3716364618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei027.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……\nご、ごめんなさい、言い過ぎました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…\nS-sorry. I went too far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3716364618,
      "endTime": 137.989028811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1994140063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "……いいのよ。あれだけ頑張ってたんだもの\n気持ちが荒れちゃうのは仕方ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s okay. You were trying so hard.\nit’s only natural to get emotional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1994140063,
      "endTime": 146.14941410170002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "なんで……なんで遙子さんは……\nそんなに、ずっと優しいんですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why… Why are you…\n…always so kind…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3597992971,
      "endTime": 154.3737904622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.3597992971
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5841756577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
